<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<p>列宁为什么说对资产阶级专政，这个问题要搞清楚。这个问题不搞清楚，就会变修正主义。要使全国知道。</p>
<p><strong>Why did Lenin speak of exercising dictatorship over the bourgeoisie? This question must be thoroughly understood. “Lack of clarity on this question will lead to revisionism. This should be made known to the whole nation.</strong></p>
</div>
